name: $start
desc: Returns: Structural variant inner start. If the coordinate system is either 0-based or 1-based, then start position is inclusive.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Structural variant inner start. If the coordinate system is either 0-based or 1-based, then start position is inclusive.

name: $end
desc: Returns: Structural variant inner end. If the coordinate system is 0-based then end is exclusive and does not include the last position. If the coordinate system is 1-base, then end is inclusive and includes the last position.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Structural variant inner end. If the coordinate system is 0-based then end is exclusive and does not include the last position. If the coordinate system is 1-base, then end is inclusive and includes the last position.
